name: Helen Yang
about: Hey, I'm Helen! I'm a freshman CS major hoping to learn about app+web dev and assistive technology. Outside of DTI, I'm also part of Science Olympiad, which I competed in while in high school. When I'm not crying about CS, you can find me playing Minesweeper and Tetris, binge-watching Bon Appetit videos, or jamming out to music ranging from classical to chiptune!
